snippet.title: La Salamanca - Official Demo Trailer | Latin American Games Showcase
snippet.description: Take a look at the demo trailer for La Salamanca, a first-person psychological horror game developed by Carpincho Studio. Players will solve puzzles, hide from what lurks in the shadows, and encounter a local legend inspired by Argentina folklore. La Salamanca is coming soon to PC (Steam) with a demo available now.
